\n    - 事件列表过滤\n    - 事件类型筛选\n    - 截图展示\n    - 快速跳转回放\n\n17. **实现 `web/src/views/SettingsView.vue`**\n    - 存储阈值滑块\n    - 检测开关\n    - 灵敏度调节\n    - 系统信息显示\n\n### 阶段3: Python检测进程\n\n18. **实现 `detection/main.py`**\n    - Unix Socket帧接收\n    - 500ms抽帧\n    - 事件HTTP回调Go API\n    - 信号处理优雅退出\n\n19. **实现 `detection/yolo.py`**\n    - YOLOv8姿态检测\n    - YOLOv8人形检测\n    - 摔倒判定算法\n    - ultralytics集成\n\n20. **实现 `detection/audio.py`**\n    - 音频频谱分析\n    - 哭声检测(1-4kHz)\n    - 异响检测(能量突变)\n    - scipy STFT支持\n\n21. **创建 `detection/requirements.txt`**\n    - torch, torchvision\n    - ultralytics, opencv\n    - numpy, scipy, Pillow\n\n### 阶段4: 配置与文档\n\n22. **创建 `go.mod`**\n    - gocv, Pion WebRTC, Gin\n    - 正确版本依赖\n\n23. **创建 `config.yaml`**\n    - 服务器端口\n    - 存储配置\n    - 采集参数\n    - 编码参数\n    - 检测开关\n\n24. **创建 `build.sh`**\n    - Go编译脚本\n    - Python检测进程打包\n\n25. **创建 `README.md`**\n    - 特性说明\n    - 快速开始\n    - 项目结构\n    - API文档\n    - 技术栈\n\n---\n\n## 产出文件列表（含路径）\n\n### Go后端\n- `/app/data/autodev/VisionLoop-----100--2026-03-2-1774439980/go.mod`\n- `/app/data/autodev/VisionLoop-----100--2026-03-2-1774439980/cmd/server/main.go`\n- `/app/data/autodev/VisionLoop-----100--2026-03-2-1774439980/internal/capture/capture.go`\n- `/app/data/autodev/VisionLoop-----100--2026-03-2-1774439980/internal/encoder/encoder.go`\n- `/app/data/autodev/VisionLoop-----100--2026-03-2-1774439980/internal/mp4/mp4.go`\n- `/app/data/autodev/VisionLoop-----100--2026-03-2-1774439980/internal/storage/gc.go`\n- `/app/data/autodev/VisionLoop-----100--2026-03-2-1774439980/internal/webrtc/webrtc.go`\n- `/app/data/autodev/VisionLoop-----100--2026-03-2-1774439980/internal/ipc/socket.go`\n- `/app/data/autodev/VisionLoop-----100--2026-03-2-1774439980/internal/api/server.go`\n\n### Vue3前端\n- `/app/data/autodev/VisionLoop-----100--2026-03-2-1774439980/web/package.json`\n- `/app/data/autodev/VisionLoop-----100--2026-03-2-1774439980/web/vite.config.js`\n- `/app/data/autodev/VisionLoop-----100--2026-03-2-1774439980/web/ind